@startuml
autonumber
box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box
box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "Flexibility Emission MS" as FlexMS
participant "Telemetry MS" as TMS
participant "Prosumer MS" as PMS
end box
box "Messaging Layer" #Thistle
queue "Kafka Topic:\nFlexibility-Offers" as KafkaFlex
end box
box "Persistence Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS\n(Flexibility DB)" as FlexDB
end box
== Flexibility Emission ==

Camunda -> Kong: Trigger FlexibilityEmission
Kong -> FlexMS: Forward request

FlexMS -> Kong: GET /assetlinks/active/{assetId}
Kong -> TMS: Forward GET /telemetry/active/{assetId}
TMS --> Kong: 200 OK {activeAssetLinks[]}
Kong --> FlexMS: 200 OK {activeAssetLinks[]}

FlexMS -> FlexMS: Apply Flexibility Rules
note right: If BESS SoC > 90% AND market price HIGH -> Trigger Sell Event\nIf BESS SoC < 20% -> Mark asset Unavailable
FlexMS -> FlexDB: JDBC INSERT flexibility_event\n(id, assetId, prosumerId, eventType, soc_percent, timestamp)
FlexDB --> FlexMS: 200 OK
FlexMS -> KafkaFlex: Publish FlexibilityEvent\n{eventId, assetId, prosumerId, eventType, timestamp}
KafkaFlex --> FlexMS: Ack
FlexMS --> Kong: 201 Created {eventId}
Kong --> Camunda: Flexibility Event Created


Loop
   PMS -> KafkaFlex: Consumes from\n Flexibility-Offers
   KafkaFlex -> PMS: JSON Payload

END

@enduml